{"title":"Bike Gear Database Interviewed John","link":"https://theradavist.com/bike-gear-database-interviewed-the-radavist/","date":1717423129000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/John_Bike-Gear-Database_Interview.jpeg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/John_Bike-Gear-Database_Interview.jpeg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/John_Bike-Gear-Database_Interview.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/John_Bike-Gear-Database_Interview.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/John_Bike-Gear-Database_Interview.jpeg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/johnprolly/\" target=\"_blank\">John</a> recently sat down with Barry from Bike Gear Database for an interview. They talked about everything from the roots of this website to photography, his “<a href=\"https://theradavist.com/my-29-titanium-sklar-pack-mule-mtb-with-tumbleweed-persuader-bars/\" target=\"_blank\">forever bike</a>,” <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/moots-womble-review/\" target=\"_blank\">black metal</a>, and more. Roll on over to <a href=\"https://www.bikegeardatabase.com/stories/john-watson\" target=\"_blank\">Bike Gear Database</a> for a behind-the-scenes peek into The Radavist’s <em>modus operandi</em>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bike-gear-database-interviewed-the-radavist/\">Bike Gear Database Interviewed John</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"359b05c5a2336ef10cea28c3b4ea05a5e79564c083e332ee7fc866dc010faf39","category":"Cycling"}